#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/building-native-image.adoc
msgid ""
"Before going further, be sure to have a working container runtime (Docker, podman) environment.\n"
"If you use Docker on Windows you should share your project's drive at Docker Desktop file share settings and restart Docker Desktop."
